title: Macro and Bitcoin Market Structure with Preston Pysh
description:
Blockware Lead Insights Analyst Will Clemente and We Study Billionares Co-Founder Preston Pysh talk about Bitcoin market dynamics, macro uncertainty, interest rates, HyperBitcoinization and more for our weekly interview Podcast/YouTube channel series. Can now find our podcast on Spotify, Apple, and Google Podcasts as well!


Preston’s twitter: twitter.com/PrestonPysh
